keyFacts: Jeffrey E. Epstein, as president of Laurel Inc., transferred property to Bliss Inc., Church Religious Organization for $200 on March 9, 2019.
The property is located in El Bravo Park, Palm Beach County, Florida, with Parcel ID 50-4343-2746-000-0391.
The deed was recorded on October 23, 2020, in Palm Beach County, Florida.
The transaction involves a religious organization (Bliss Inc., Church Religious Organization) as the grantee.
The document shows Epstein's involvement in corporate property transactions in 2019, after his 2008 conviction.
